These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  paramedic, entrepreneur, analystcher, police-officer, bartender, nurse, analyst
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bongani, fonseca, cain, tiparillo, game, dunhill
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, punk, ambient, disco, jazz, soul, gospel
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, bird, horse, frog, turtle, rat
 1. the fan disco is on the far right##1
 2. the fan jazz is the cain-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the frog is the fan ambient##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the entrepreneur is the fan ambient##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the rat and the game-smoker##2
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the analystcher is in the middle##1
11. the fan r&b is the bartender##1
12. the bartender is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
13. the paramedic is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
14. the game-smoker is the owner of the bird##1
15. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
16. the entrepreneur is on the left of the nurse##1
17. the fan soul is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
18. the analyst is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
19. the fan gospel is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Job      | entrepreneur  | nurse        | bartender | analystcher      | police-officer     | paramedic      | analyst     |
| Cigar   | bongani | cain         | dunhill   | siglo | game    | tiparillo | fonseca |
| Music-Genre         | ambient | jazz | r&b | punk | gospel  | soul  | disco    |
| Pet     | frog  | turtle         | guinea-pig     | rabbit    | bird | horse     | rat     |

